data.description: Very nice two stories home in a quite established neighborhood. Built in 2008, fresh coat of paint, home sits at the end of court, minimal traffic, open concept living, dining and kitchen. Featuring ceramic title in the kitchen and bathrooms, wood floor in the living area and carpet on all bedrooms, kitchen breakfast bar and plenty of cabinet and counter space, recessed lighting, half bath on the 1st floor. Full size utilities room, large back yard fully landscaped with sprinkler system.
